OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and occasional showers this
OL,7,Fevening. The showers most frequent in
OL,8,Fthe west and around the north coast
OL,9,Fovernight, some drier and clearer
OL,10,Fspells for Belfast and the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,13,Fbest of the brightness across Counties
OL,14,FAntrim and Down during the morning.
OL,15,FThe showers could be heavy, perhaps
OL,16,Fthe odd rumble of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
