OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand bright start on Monday, rain then
OL,7,Fpushing in from the southwest.
OL,8,FBrihtening up with scattered showers
OL,9,Fon Tuesday. Mainly dry on Wednesday.
